- `home_screen_refresh` - Logs pull-to-refresh with data availability status
- `home_screen_first_load` - Tracks initial screen load with timestamp
- `home_question_progress_loaded` - Logs question progress data with solve counts
- `home_calendar_data_loaded` - Tracks calendar data with streak and activity metrics
- `home_badges_loaded` - Logs badge data with count information
- `home_no_contest_participation` - Tracks users with no contest history
- `home_no_badges` - Logs when users have no badges

**LoginScreenPortrait.kt Analytics Events:**
- `screen_view` - Tracks when users enter the login screen
- `login_update_status_changed` - Logs app update status changes
- `login_no_update_needed` - Tracks when no app update is required
- `login_optional_update_shown` - Logs optional update dialog display
- `login_update_dialog_dismissed` - Tracks when users dismiss update dialogs
- `login_update_dialog_confirmed` - Logs when users confirm app updates
- `login_update_store_not_found` - Tracks when Play Store app is not available
- `login_force_update_shown` - Logs forced update scenarios
- `login_update_check_error` - Tracks update check failures
- `login_update_status_null` - Logs null update status states

**OnboardingScreenPortrait.kt Analytics Events:**
- `screen_view` - Tracks when users enter the onboarding screen
- `onboarding_username_validation` - Logs username validation results with length
- `onboarding_username_validation_started` - Tracks when validation process begins
- `onboarding_username_changed` - Logs username input changes with metrics
- `onboarding_continue_clicked` - Tracks continue button clicks with user context
- `onboarding_guest_user_clicked` - Logs guest user selection
- `onboarding_create_account_clicked` - Tracks external account creation attempts

All events include relevant parameters for detailed analytics insights, such as user states, validation results, data availability, and interaction contexts."}]}]}
